{"word":"θαυμάζω","slug":"θαυμάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϑαυμάζω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prec.\">prec.</a>] ‘be extraordinarily impressed’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> <b>to wonder, be amazed/astonished/impressed/surprised <a href='B:470 8:10'>Mt 8:10</a>; <a href='B:480 15:5'>Mk 15:5</a>; <a href='B:490 1:21'>Lk 1:21</a>; <a href='B:490 8:25'>8:25</a>; <a href='B:490 11:38'>11:38</a>; <a href='B:500 4:27'>J 4:27</a>; <a href='B:500 7:15'>7:15</a>; <a href='B:510 3:12'>Ac 3:12</a>; <a href='B:550 1:6'>Gal 1:6</a>; <a href='B:690 3:13'>1 J 3:13</a>; <a href='B:730 17:6'>Rv 17:6f</a>;</b> in response to miracles <b><a href='B:470 9:33'>Mt 9:33</a>; <a href='B:470 21:20'>21:20</a>; <a href='B:490 9:43'>Lk 9:43</a>; <a href='B:500 7:21'>J 7:21</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ tr.\">tr.</a> <b>admire, wonder at, be surprised about <a href='B:490 7:9'>Lk 7:9</a>; <a href='B:490 24:12'>24:12</a>; <a href='B:500 5:28'>J 5:28</a>; <a href='B:510 7:31'>Ac 7:31</a>; <a href='B:600 1:10'>2 Th 1:10</a>;</b> <el>ϑαυμάζειν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρόσωπον\">πρόσωπον</a></el> court persons <b><a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 16</a>.</b> Pass. in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b>wonder, be amazed <a href='B:730 17:8'>Rv. 17:8</a>; <a href='B:730 13:3'>13:3</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:θαῦμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:θαυμάσιος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}